column5: I just got invited by my father for a week trip up on Lac Seul this coming August 20-26. Unfortunately, I don't know where on the lake we are at as it is not a resort, but a private cabin so I don't have any idea on where to look. Maybe as I get some more specifics I can update what I find out in order to get some better feedback. Any kind of general info on the lake during the listed time frame you can give? Thanks.
Go too search and type in Lac Seul....lots of info avaliable. Go to Lac Seul ...you wont regret it.
